2
00:00:47,647 --> 00:00:49,079
because of nightmares...
被惡夢驚醒

3
00:00:49,080 --> 00:00:50,335
and in my dreams I see
在惡夢裡我看到

4
00:00:50,435 --> 00:00:51,600
how my mother died.
我媽是怎麼死的

5
00:00:51,920 --> 00:00:55,140
She died when she was going to buy
她死在去商店

6
00:00:55,240 --> 00:00:57,479
something in a shop...
買東西的路上

7
00:00:57,480 --> 00:00:59,786
I was slowly following her because
我在後面跟著她，

8
00:00:59,886 --> 00:01:02,079
I wasn't wearing any shoes.
但我沒有穿鞋所以我走得很慢

9
00:01:02,080 --> 00:01:03,844
When she crossed the main road
當她過馬路的時候

10
00:01:03,944 --> 00:01:05,279
a car ran her over.
一台車從她身上開輾過

11
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:07,040
So she fell to the floor
於是她倒在地上、

12
00:01:07,140 --> 00:01:09,119
and all her guts were out.
她的腸子都跑出來

13
00:01:09,120 --> 00:01:11,930
and all the things she held in her hands
所有她拿在手上的東西

14
00:01:12,030 --> 00:01:13,639
flew all over the place.
也飛散四周

15
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:16,194
So when I remember this kind of things
當我想起這些事情，

16
00:01:16,294 --> 00:01:18,239
I throw money into the air.
我會把錢都丟到空中

17
00:01:40,600 --> 00:01:41,440
Hey.
哈囉

18
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:43,880
What do you want?
你想幹嘛？

19
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:47,720
I'm looking for a place to sleep.
我在找可以睡覺過夜的地方

20
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:49,160
Where are you from?
你從哪邊來的？

21
00:01:49,520 --> 00:01:51,000
Mekele.

22
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:54,440
Do you have any family?
你有任何家人嗎？

23
00:01:55,320 --> 00:01:58,040
No, my parents are dead.
沒有，我父母都過世了

24
00:01:58,040 --> 00:02:00,840
If you want to sleep here you'll have to pay.
如果你想在這裡過夜你得付錢

25
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:02,640
How much?
多少錢？

26
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:05,080
Show me how much you got.
給我看你有多少錢

27
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:15,880
Now, just go away and don't come back.
好了你滾吧、不要再回來

28
00:02:15,880 --> 00:02:17,840
Give me back my money.
把錢還我

29
00:02:18,200 --> 00:02:19,080
Go away!
走開！

30
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:22,840
I said go away!
我叫你走開！

31
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:25,540
Please, give me back my money.
拜託！請把錢還我

32
00:02:25,640 --> 00:02:26,159
Go away!
走開！

33
00:02:26,160 --> 00:02:28,480
I don´t have anything left, please...
那是我僅剩的一切了,拜託…

34
00:02:28,480 --> 00:02:31,560
Go!
滾！

35
00:02:32,200 --> 00:02:32,840
Go!
滾！

36
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:36,099
