我會用這根棍子打爆你的頭！

38
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,846
I used to live in Mekele with my stepmother
我本來跟我繼母一起住在Mekele

39
00:04:45,946 --> 00:04:47,439
because I don't have my own parents anymore.
因為我雙親都過世了

40
00:04:48,440 --> 00:04:52,382
My stepmother hit me every day so one night
我繼母每天都會打我、

41
00:04:52,482 --> 00:04:55,353
I decided to steal 150 birr
有一天我偷了150比爾

42
00:04:55,453 --> 00:04:57,478
and ran away from home.
就逃家了

43
00:04:58,960 --> 00:05:00,790
I was looking for a truck going to
後來我找到一輛要去

44
00:05:00,890 --> 00:05:02,720
Addis Abeba and I found one.
Addis Abeba 的卡車

45
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:05,040
I hid inside the truck´s trailer...
我躲在後面的拖車裡

46
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:06,520
the trailer was so full
因為拖車很滿，

47
00:05:06,620 --> 00:05:08,254
that it was going dead slow
所以速度很慢，

48
00:05:08,354 --> 00:05:10,599
so it was easy to run and hide in it.
很容易就跳上去了

49
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:15,920
And that's how I arrived to Addis Abeba.
這也是我怎麼到Addis Abeba這裡來的

50
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:19,480
And ended up in the streets...
這也是我怎麼到這裡來的

51
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:38,405
Let's finish this chat
我們差不多了，

52
00:07:38,505 --> 00:07:42,199
and go find some business for the night.
去為今晚找點賺頭吧

53
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:53,774
How do you feel now?
你現在覺得如何？

54
00:07:53,874 --> 00:07:55,399
Are you still high?
還很嗨嘛？

55
00:07:55,400 --> 00:07:56,618
Not so much, 
現在沒了，

56
00:07:56,718 --> 00:07:59,839
