My friend stole lot´s of money...
我朋友昨天偷了一大筆錢...

58
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:06,880
How did he do it?
他怎麼做到的？

59
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:09,119
He was begging so a guy took out
他在行乞，

60
00:08:09,219 --> 00:08:11,519
1 birr from his pocket...
有個傢伙想給他1 比爾，

61
00:08:11,520 --> 00:08:14,320
