Hey kid! Give us back the stick!
嘿小子！把棍子還來！

102
00:11:50,360 --> 00:11:51,303
Hey, kid, give it to us,
小子！把棍子還我們！

103
00:11:51,403 --> 00:11:52,959
can't you see he can't walk without it!
他沒有那個不能走路你看不出來嘛！

104
00:11:54,720 --> 00:11:55,554
Give me back my money then,
那把錢還我！

105
00:11:55,654 --> 00:11:57,159
 I don´t have anything. Can´t you see that?!
我什麼都沒有了你看不出來嘛！

106
00:11:57,160 --> 00:11:59,280
We don´t have anything either!
我們也什麼都沒有阿！

107
00:11:59,280 --> 00:12:00,920
I don't have any family.
但是我連家人都沒有了

108
00:12:00,920 --> 00:12:03,600
Neither do us!
我們也沒有阿！

109
00:12:03,840 --> 00:12:05,760
I'm going to sell the stick to get some food.
我要把這跟棍子賣掉換點食物

110
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:08,320
Sell it? Give it back to me now!
賣掉？你給我還來喔！

111
00:12:08,320 --> 00:12:10,520
He cannot walk without the stick!
他這樣真的不能走路！

112
00:12:10,520 --> 00:12:11,779
Give back the stick!
棍子還來！

113
00:12:11,879 --> 00:12:13,559
